1. *Istom* se brzinom kretao i on i njegov brat. (He and his brother moved at the same speed.)
2. Cela obitelj je bila zabrinuta zbog *istog* problema. (The whole family was worried about the same problem.)
3. Ona je istih misli kao i ja. (She has the same thoughts as me.)
4. Svi su bili uvjereni u *istu* stvar. (Everyone was convinced of the same thing.)
5. Ona je odgovarala *isto* pitanje tri puta. (She answered the same question three times.)